---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="About — kafkade" description="About kafkade — software creator, reader, builder.">
  <section class="py-8">
    <h1 class="text-[1.4rem] font-bold mb-6">About</h1>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-[0.9rem] text-[--color-text-muted] leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I'm <strong class="text-[--color-text] font-semibold">kafkade</strong> — a software creator based near the
        Cascade mountains. I build tools, explore systems, and write about what I learn along the way.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-[1.1rem] font-bold text-[--color-text] pt-4">The Name</h2>
      <p>
        <em>kafkade</em> is a portmanteau of <strong class="text-[--color-text]">Kafka</strong> — as in Franz Kafka, whose writing
        explores the absurd, the bureaucratic, and the deeply human — and <strong class="text-[--color-text]">Cascade</strong>,
        the mountain range that defines the Pacific Northwest landscape where I live and work.
      </p>
      <p>
        It's a name that sits between literature and terrain, between thinking and building.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-[1.1rem] font-bold text-[--color-text] pt-4">What I Do</h2>
      <p>
        I build software. I care about clean code, thoughtful architecture, and tools that
        respect their users. Most of my work is open source and lives on GitHub.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-[1.1rem] font-bold text-[--color-text] pt-4">Connect</h2>
      <p>
        <a href="https://github.com/kafkade" class="accent">GitHub</a><span class="text-[--color-sage] mx-1">·</span>
        <a href="https://x.com/kafkade33926" class="accent">Twitter</a><span class="text-[--color-sage] mx-1">·</span>
        <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/kafkadev.bsky.social" class="accent">Bluesky</a><span class="text-[--color-sage] mx-1">·</span>
        <a href="https://patreon.com/c/kafkade" class="accent">Patreon</a><span class="text-[--color-sage] mx-1">·</span>
        <a href="https://buymeacoffee.com/kafkade" class="accent">Buy Me a Coffee</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
